      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and sophistication. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, it remains in commendable condition, offering a seamless blend of performance and prestige. This is an investment in quality that transcends the ordinary, maintained to a standard that ensures immediate road-readiness.",
